OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mix of sunny spells and
OL,6,Fshowers, the showers heavy at times
OL,7,Fwith a risk of thunder. The showers
OL,8,Fbecoming a little lighter and less
OL,9,Ffrequent this afternoon. Occasionally
OL,10,Fstrong northerly winds. Rather cold.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FSome late sunny spells, then
OL,13,Fclear spells overnight, with showers,
OL,14,Fthese becoming fewer and lighter as
OL,15,Fthe night goes on. Touch of frost
OL,16,Fpossible in sheltered spots.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
