OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA few morning showers with
OL,6,Fsunny spells, but the afternoon looks
OL,7,Fdry with some longer spells of
OL,8,Fsunshine. Still rather cold with
OL,9,Fnorthwesterly winds remaining
OL,10,Foccasionally strong in coastal parts.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry
OL,13,Fwith sunny spells Saturday, perhaps
OL,14,Fsome evening rain. Overnight rain soon
OL,15,Fclearing Sunday then sunny spells and
OL,16,Fa few showers. Rather cloudy Monday
OL,17,Fwith a little rain. Becoming milder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
